{"tid":447243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【博上鏡】熱心警察幫市民執紙皮獲網民激讚","createTime":"2017-10-25T06:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-25T06:36:41.000Z","uid":2547,"like":4,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"34c6ffb0c6ab19b0f47e6058ae1f2b39cfc05c15","tid":447243,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:07:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TRI3lRhnqzc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTRI3lRhnqzc&d=oxtiZK7xqkTTCE5WOLx4A5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=efe16096\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TRI3lRhnqzc</a><br />\n<br />\n近日網上流傳一段影片，一名交通警上前協助一名推著紙皮的市民執拾散落地下的紙皮，過程被附近司機拍下並分享至網絡，獲網民激讚，直言要寫信表揚這位警員的善行。<br />\n<br />\n有網民於 Facebook 群組「香港交通突發報料區」分享影片，指昨日下午四時左右何文田天光道上，一名推著紙皮車的市民疑似於上落斜路時發生意外，車上的紙皮散落地上，一名交通警員將電單車停下，上前彎腰協助對方執拾地上的紙皮，並將紙皮疊好。<br />\n<br />\n網民留言：<br />\n<br />\n「呢啲係好基本嘅品行，我反而想知，點解有時間拍片都唔落去幫手」<br />\n<br />\n「如知道交通警車牌可以去信表揚一下」<br />\n<br />\n「呢個阿 sir 抵讃」<br />\n<br />\n「世界有好多種人 有好有壞 見到有人做好事係要俾like 香港多d正能量係好事」<br />\n<br />\n「佢幫手係正常」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5毛大軍全面打飛機"},{"pid":"ef829e7f473d7a640cee605f4af5802b41a5b3da","tid":447243,"uid":143260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:10:23.000Z","msg":"婆婆執紙皮又唔見班五毛友寫熱心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911d07eb93f91dc539f6685eb25c2cad2c659b7d","tid":447243,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-25T06:11:47.000Z","msg":"過兩日就幫食環狗打柒個阿婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54c8